data.description: Supremely stylish and upgraded, this exquisite single-family residence boasts designer finishes throughout its four bedrooms and three bathrooms, offering ample space and luxury for comfortable living.  Upon entering, you're greeted by a welcoming open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with family.  The modern kitchen is a chef's delight - actually functional with plenty of counterspace, walk-in pantry, and so much storage!  Your primary bedroom is a serene retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom featuring a luxurious soaking tub, separate shower, and dual sinks. Three additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests, home office space, or a growing family. Step outside to the beautifully landscaped backyard oasis, ideal for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the California sunshine. With a patio area perfect for BBQs and a low-maintenance turf lawn, this backyard is sure to be your favorite spot for relaxation!Conveniently located in the desirable master-planned Escaya at Otay Ranch community, this home offers easy access to shopping, dining, parks, and top-rated schools. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stunning property your own. Schedule a showing today and envision yourself living the ultimate California lifestyle at 1332 Camino Carmelo!
